column8: Hey boyo watch where you throw those fireballs of yours, cause they wreak a lot of havoc, and I end up having to clean up after, you understand? But if someone gives you grief, you got my permission to chuck one right in his eye!
Nice place you got up here, boyo! Though enough with the small talk already, let's get on with the sparring practice! Go on, let me have it, give me everything you got!!
Want a piece of me boyo?
Think you can take me boyo?
What can I do for you?
Can I help you, or what?
Ooh change of plan I like it!
Want to try that thing out?
You using that thing now huh?
Ooh would you look at that.
Pretty mean knife you got there.
That some kind of fishing pole or what?
Scared to get up close and personal, boyo?
What'd you get, what'd you get?
Time for a break there, pal?
So you want to give it a rest, or what?
All right, pal, you can stop!
Anytime you want to stop, there, boyo.
How am I supposed to get back?
Don't think I'm supposed to be here.
Uh kind of stuck here, pal.
Hah, haha, bet I got you pretty good!
Hahah, bet I got you pretty good!
Haw, just what I always wanted, there, besides getting smacked around for no good reason! I'll take that off your hands, all right, but let me give you this!
Look at this guy over here.
Hey think there's something for you over there.
Something you ought to check out over there.
...I mean, Achilles, pal, look I don't want to bust your chops or anything, but all I'm saying here, is, personally? I never took a shot to the ankle or whatever, back when I was alive!
Hoh, I was something else, all right, you should have seen me! I could take anybody on the isle, blindfolded!
<Ah! Oof! Augh! Ungh. Waw! Brlrl! Bwuh! Ungh! Woo!>
Good, just the boyo I wanted to see, c'mere!
Oh, have I got something for you, boyo!
Get a load of them prizes over there.
Hah you did it, boyo! Reward's right over there!
She sure is! Isn't she beautiful!
Whoa-hoh you earned yourself another one, congrats!
Well I'll be a hellhound's hindquarters, you really pulled it off.
Because, pal, you are a discerning individual!
And have I mentioned that it cost a lot of coin?
It weighs an awful lot, too.
I know what you mean pal.
I was just thinking the same.
You got taste, pal, I will give you that.
Only the best for you, pal.
That is an excellent interpretation boyo.
I see exactly what you mean.
I knew you would appreciate that aspect.
Whoa don't you touch that thing!
That is a priceless work of art there pal!
Hey, don't you scratch that thing, boyo!
Go fill out that form you got.
I don't make the rules, pal.
Got to sign up for this contest.
Think you got what it takes?!
Come on, pal, live a little!
Nuh-uh, you gotta work for it!
Special delivery for you back there, boyo!
Keep your finger on the trigger at all times, pal.
Nothing to it, pal, just point and shoot.
Know how to use that thing?
You got a license for that thing?
Might want to check your stash of weapons over there...
Hey what's going on back there?
What's all the racket over there?
You all right back there pal?
What kind of sorcery was that?
Never felt a cut like that before!
Love what you've done to your sword!
That bow's got a different sting to it!
New arrows or something there pal?
Your shield's looking pretty handsome pal!
I get the feeling I am being watched...?
Never been stabbed quite like that!
Felt all three points on that spear, pal!
Hey that shot felt different somehow!
You been messing with that shooty thing pal?
Uh, might want to see this, boyo, over to my left?
Look what they did to your pink window, pal!!
Hey, the Pact lit up, you must have done something!
What you need more practice, pal?
Just go, pal. You can do it.
Go on, boyo, get out of here.
Don't stick around on my account, boyo.
Need another fancy weapon there or what?
What do you need there pal?
Care for a warm-up with that?
Bet you couldn't hit me with that, pal.
Time to give that thing some work I guess.
You be careful with that one boyo.
I got your chopping block right here, pal.
Stick it to me, boyo, come on!
Just watch the ribs with that, OK?
Go on and clock me with that if you want.
I still don't get what that's supposed to be.
Give me one of them arrows right in the eye!
Couple of practice shots or something?
Go on, boyo, shoot me, let's see you do it!
How about you give me your best shot!
Bet you can't hit me repeatedly from there.
Hey, pal, uh, wanted to talk to you...
That's it... the blade... you got to let me have it with that thing.
Come on, bozo, pick on someone your own size!
Whoever kills me gets a big promotion!
Ah boyo this place is a mess!
Whoa nice place to stand around!
Got here just as soon as I was able, pal!
Hah what a bunch of bozos!!
Look at all these guys, come on!
Heeey bozo, let's see what you got!
You bozos look like you could use some practice!
You mess with my pal, you mess with me!
I'll hold them off, boyo, you do your thing!
Forget about me, boyo! Save yourself!
Oh I got your back, there, pal!
Well my work here is done.
Look at the size of that thing!
Hey Thanatos, big fan right here!
You need a skeleton to stand around?
Be there in just a second or two, pal!
I shall answer the call, boyo!
I hear you, pal, hang on!
It's time to get beat up!
Don't need to tell me twice!
I'm back, what did I miss?
Oh I will be right back!
Be back in just a sec!
Whoa it is hot in here!
Hey look at all that magma!
Whoa, look at all of this!
Whoa this place is a dump!
The air feels weird up here!
Hey pick on somebody my size!
Think you can break these bones?
Nyah, come get me and all that!
Hope I don't die and drop this precious loot!
You don't have what it takes!!
Hey, may I have your attention for a sec?
Come on, you bozos, do it!
I'm here, kill me, you bozos!
Come on, kill me, you goofs!
Come on, kill me, I'm here!!
Come on, do it, kill me!!
You want a piece of me you guys?!
Come on, you bozos, let's see what you got!
Got some real fancy bozos over here!
These guys don't look so tough!
Oh I can take a hit!!
Come give me your best shot!!
What if I beg for mercy, huh?
Pssh I could hit harder than that!
You haven't seen the last of me!!
Hey go check on your pointy spear boyo!
Whoa what in the world is that?
More of a slicing feel there rather than a stabbing!
I'll just hang out a while.
I, uh... I'll just be over here.
What, you going to sock it to me, pal?
Hey, uh, something back there for you, pal!
What, you going to sock it to me, pal?
Yeah, give me your best shot!
Hoh now that's a shiny bow you got right there!
Yeoow that's got a nice little kick of heat to it!
Hooh now that's what I call getting shot by arrows!
Your serving platter, what did you just do?
Uh that's no shooty thing I recognize.
Ooh, nice burning sensation from that!
If you did, pal, I would not be here right now!
Yeah, no, that definitely wouldn't fly.
I feel exactly the same way.
Can't get over how tall they are!
I can't get over it, myself.
Oof, I felt that deep down in my jaw!
Hey who turned out the lights?!
You keep that whip away from my pal!
So, what's going on between you two?
Hey you big lug, over here!
Hey Big-Bones, want some of this?!
Why'd you drag me into this one, pal?!
Nice bone structure on that thing over there!
Hey, bull boy, what's the matter?
Ooh, help, he's got a double bladed axe!
The king of Athens, I'm so scared, boyo!

column6: Referring to having an audience (and we can make the crowd cheer)

column8: This one's for you guys out in the cheap seats!
Looks like I made it for the big event!

column6: Nodding her head at an associate.
column8: Hey Thanatos, big fan right here!
Uh, must have taken a wrong turn somewhere!
Hey, what you doing all the way up here?
Whoa it's Papa, you're in trouble, pal!
Think this one's between you and Papa, pal!

column6: Gag version of Zag's similar line.
column8: You beat me, I'll just keep coming back!
Go on and sock it to me, here!
Can't even kill an unarmed skeleton!
How about a stationary target for a change?
Want me to move, make me!
Come give me your best shot!
Oh, help me, boyo, I'm so scared!

column6: Gag version of Zag's similar line.
column8: You know who you're dealing with?
Eugh, what happened to your mitts, boyo?

column6: Response to first death, punked you

column8: All that damage, that was nothing, pal!
